{
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.char": "这里是哪里哇？怎么还有一头大鲸鱼哇！？",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.next": "惊讶",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.ancient": "[sine]...可爱... 去塔里... ..有你的... 答案.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "[sine]...你...回来了..... \n...蓝发... ..小女孩.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.ancient": "[sine]...你.. 需要... ..什么...？[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.next": "难过",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.char": "为什么又失败了哇。",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-2.ancient": "[sine]...别怕...我会... \n..一直... 在...这里... ..帮你.....[/sine]",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.char": "哇...好多小东西哇！就像小灯的房间一样。",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.ancient": "那是谁？也和我一样收集了很多被遗忘的宝石吗？",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "你又来了？挑一件和你故友一样的宝石回去吧！",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.ancient": "我这里有无数宝石，但从没见过你说的那件！",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.next": "回应",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.char": "小灯还收集了好多可爱的石头哇！\n以后有机会我带给你看看！",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-2.ancient": "哈哈。我会等着的，虽然“下次”可能得等很久了。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.char": "贵安！这里好优雅哇！",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.ancient": "哎呀，终于来了个懂我的小女孩，让我赐予你优雅的力量吧。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "可怜的小女孩，建筑师又把你赶下去了吗。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0r.ancient": "不要如此灰头土脸呀。让我帮你擦擦。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0r.next": "婉拒",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1r.char": "没关系哇！我会继续努力的！",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1r.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-2r.ancient": "真是个努力的小女孩。拿去吧。让我看看你穿着新衣服的样子。",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.char": "贵安……!你好漂亮哇。",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.ancient": "可爱小女孩！！很高兴见到你！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "小故事！！小故事！！这次还想要听！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.char": "你好喜欢哇，那我再讲一次独角仙的故事哇！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.ancient": "想要什么？“钢琴”的声音！？那是什么？！想听想听！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.next": "弹奏",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.char": "mi re do re mi fa mi re~",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-2.ancient": "好！！好！！钢琴！！好听！！",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.char": "……贵安？",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.ancient": "[thinky_dots]可爱的小女孩……拿走我的一部分，让我继续睡吧……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "[thinky_dots]你看起来很累……你也睡一会儿吧……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]拿走我的血肉吧……就当是你可爱的奖励……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.next": "回答",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.char": "……不痛吗？佩尔先生，我拿走了哇……？",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-2.ancient": "[thinky_dots]收下吧……能帮到你这么可爱的小女孩……也能做个好梦了[/thinky_dots]",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.char": "贵安！你看起来好强大哇！！！",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.ancient": "[b]哈哈！！真是可爱！！[/b]\n[b]拿着这把武器吧！！能和我一样变强！！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "[b]你看起来有点疲倦了！但战斗能让你沸腾起来！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.ancient": "[b]小女孩！！与我一战！！看看你的成长！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.next": "用尽全力",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.char": "呜哇，根本打不动哇...\n[i][font_size=22]小祥坐在地上，喘着大气。[/font_size][/i]",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-2.ancient": "[b]软弱！！但你的可爱也是一种力量！！[/b]\n[b]收下这把武器吧！！可爱的小女孩！！[/b]",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.char": "贵安。这里好温暖哇...",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.ancient": "哈哈，那让我再给你的心[jitter][b]温暖[/b][/jitter]一下吧。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "哎呀...你似乎[jitter][b]背负[/b][/jitter]太多东西了？要不要让我帮你烧掉呀？",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.ancient": "小祥，来尝尝我给你做的[jitter][b]红茶[/b][/jitter]吧。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.next": "喜悦",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.char": "……谢谢特兹卡塔拉哇！真是让人怀念哇。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-2.ancient": "真是可爱，然后我们继续等到苦味[jitter][b]散尽[/b][/jitter]吧。",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.char": "贵安。请问你是恶魔先生吗？",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.ancient": "哈哈，你可以叫我[sine]瓦库[/sine]，可爱的小女孩。",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "本来我是想要卖贵些的。可面对你，[sine]“打折”[/sine]似乎变成了常态。",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.ancient": "让我们写个契约吧！允许你[sine]某一天回去[/sine]——你签么？",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0.next": "回应",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.char": "……这次又想骗我什么哇！",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-2.ancient": "在这无聊的地方，有个[sine]可爱的小女孩[/sine]真的很让人开心。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-attack": "攻击",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0r.char": "贵安，我想要回去原来的世界哇！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1r.ancient": "你是谁？我怎么一点印象都没有。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1r.next": "回答",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-2r.char": "什么意思哇……？不可以吗",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-2r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-3r.ancient": "莫名其妙，这塔里的怪事越来越多了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-3r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-4r.ancient": "我根本不懂你在说什么。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "很好，你又回来了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-1r.char": "我要…打败你哇！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-2r.ancient": "愚蠢。你那打败我就能回去的奇怪念头从哪儿来的。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0r.ancient": "为什么？就凭那个虚无缥缈的声音？我和你无冤无仇。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1r.char": "我的朋友……还在等着我哇！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1r-attack": "攻击",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.2-2r.ancient": "固执无比。",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.title": "“丰川祥子？”",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.epithet": "如梦般的幻影",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.ANY.0-0r.ancient": "贵安！请问你愿意和我一起组乐队吗？",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.firstVisitEver.0-0.ancient": "贵安！请问你愿意和我一起组乐队吗？",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.ancient": "贵安！你好呀！",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.next": "继续",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-0.char": "这...这是什么哇",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.ancient": "嗯？你看上去好像不太好哇",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.next": "继续",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-1.char": "（视线模糊）",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.0-2.ancient": "呜哇！别哭哇！",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.ancient": "贵安！我们又见面了呢！",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.next": "继续",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-0r.char": "贵安（抱住）",
  "CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_EVENT_ANOTHER_SELF.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_SAKI.1-1r.ancient": "辛苦了哇，这次我也会好好帮你的！",

  
  
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.char": "啊！好大的鲸鱼！",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.next": "惊讶",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.ancient": "[sine]...去塔里...找建筑师...[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-2.char": "会说话的大鲸鱼！啊！！好神奇！",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-2.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-3.char": "你好呀你好呀！你是怎么做到一头大鲸鱼还可以说话的？",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-3.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-4.char": "话说这里竟然会有这么高的塔啊。好壮观！",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-4.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-5.char": "你是这里的守护者吗？还是魔王的前锋队长？！",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-5.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-6.ancient": "[sine]...你...好吵...[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0.ancient": "[sine]...你怎么...回来了..... \n...吵闹的...小女孩.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-1.char": "呜呜，建筑师简直不讲理...",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-2.char": "我明明什么都还没说呢。",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-3.char": "他就突然开始攻击我！",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-4.char": "我又没有惹过他生气！！！",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-5.char": "我讨厌这个建筑师！！！",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-5.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-6.ancient": "[sine].....噢...[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0r.ancient": "[sine]...可爱的....粉色小女孩..\n 需要... ..帮忙...？[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0r.next": "难过",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1r.char": "我讨厌死建筑师了....！",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1r.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-2r.ancient": "[sine]...别生气...我们... \n....一起...击败... 他.....[/sine]",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.char": "哇...这里有好多亮闪闪的东西！",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.ancient": "哈哈。你是个有品位的女孩，来挑一挑吧！",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0r.ancient": "你回来了？这次又要挑选哪一件呢？",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.ancient": "小女孩，我发现你的话越来越多了！",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.next": "回应",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.char": "呜哇！关系好了就忍不住多说了几句。",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-2.ancient": "哈哈。没事，听你闹腾其实也感觉不坏。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.char": "呜哇！这里！好大！！！",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.ancient": "哎呀，好可爱的小女孩，想要变得更漂亮吗？",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-2.char": "想要！！！",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-3.char": "呜哇！这个衣服也好漂亮！！！",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-4.char": "如果我带回去绝对能[pink]引人注目[/pink]！",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-4.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-5.ancient": "真是活泼，喜欢就带走它吧。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0r.ancient": "可爱的小女孩，建筑师竟然嫌弃你吵闹吗。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0r.ancient": "哎呀哎呀，怎么又弄得这么狼狈。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0r.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1r.char": "路上的那些人真的一点都不懂礼貌！",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1r.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-2r.ancient": "好啦好啦，是他们不懂得优雅之道。",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.char": "哇哇哇！这是什么！！！好漂亮！！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.ancient": "很高兴见到你！！！粉色的小女孩！！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-2.char": "你也是这里的先古之民吗？",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-3.char": "这里也太漂亮了！！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-4.char": "你也好可爱！！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-4.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-5.ancient": "你也好可爱！！！我喜欢你！！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0r.ancient": "你来啦！！！好多话的小女孩！！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0r.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0r.char": "我来啦！！！我和你说，这次我又遇到了什么...",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.ancient": "可爱的小女孩！！！送你这个！！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.char": "哇！！！这个好漂亮！！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-2.ancient": "你喜欢就好！！！",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.char": "……你好？",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.ancient": "[thinky_dots]……嘘……要什么自己拿吧……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0r.ancient": "[thinky_dots]你看起来很活泼……也许睡一会儿更好……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]……你很懂礼貌……拿走这些吧……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.char": "[thinky_dots]……好……我会小声的……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-2.ancient": "[thinky_dots]……你是个可爱的好女孩……祝你也能做个好梦……[/thinky_dots]",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.char": "哇！！！好大！！！",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.ancient": "[b]哈哈！！我确实很强大！！[/b]\n[b]来！！这把武器送给你！！能和我一样变强！！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0r.ancient": "[b]你看起来很活泼！！！来和我战斗一场吧！！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.ancient": "[b]哈哈！！虽然你的力气很小！！但是内心很强大！！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.char": "真的吗！！",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-2.char": "谢谢你！！！！",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-2.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-3.ancient": "[b]接着！！！这把武器可以让你的身体也强大起来！！！\n可爱的小女孩！！[/b]",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.char": "你好~！！！啊！！好香",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.char": "啊！！！好香！！！是什么味道？！",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-2.ancient": "哈哈，要不要来喝喝试试，这[jitter][b]温暖[/b][/jitter]的美汤。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0r.ancient": "哎呀...你回来啦？来喝一下[jitter][b]暖暖[/b][/jitter]的美汤吧？",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.ancient": "呵呵...你还是这么[jitter][b]活泼[/b][/jitter]呢。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.char": "特兹卡塔拉谢谢你！！我还想要上次喝的那个！！",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-2.ancient": "哈哈，那在这期间陪我多聊聊天吧，\n还想多听你[jitter][b]说说话[/b][/jitter]。",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.char": "哇！！你长得就像是恶魔一样！！",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-0.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.ancient": "[sine]瓦库[/sine]，请这么称呼我。",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-1.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-2.char": "所以你是恶魔吗？",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.1-0r.ancient": "你要是能消停会儿，我就给你[sine]“打折”[/sine]。",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.ancient": "我想和你签个契约了，[sine]话少点[/sine]——怎么样？",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-0.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.char": "啊！！你个坏恶魔！！",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-1.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.2-2.ancient": "哈哈，逗逗你而已，\n在这荒凉的地方，有人[sine]说说话[/sine]也很不错了。",

  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.CUTE_SAKIKO_MOD_CHARACTER_CUTE_ANON.0-attack": "攻击",
